<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Entie Hukdampa chu a pui tau,
 A linglukhuk tawh;
 Dogal simsen loh te'n masawm,
 Kalvari tang tiengin.

[V2]
 Ka gitloh ziekun Na thuok ie,
 Na ul thisan bangin a vai;
 Na aw nem deihum tak pawt chu,
 Ka lunggil in ka ngilh thei puoi.

[V3]
 2. Ka en ngam puoi ka Lalpa deihtak,
 Dogal te'n zep ui;
 A thawk natzie ka genthei puoi,
 Kei di'n A hin a piei

[V4]
 3. Thihna huoisie tak A thawk lai khan,
 Kuon a panpih em?
 &quot;He pa, he pa!&quot; tiin A kiko,
 Gausapna thing chungah.

[V5]
 4. Aw ka thagau, Hukdampa thihna,
 Zion ah chieh in;
 Ziechun ngaihdamna chu mu'n la,
 A thisan apat chun.</lyrics>
<title>Entie Hukdampa chuh</title>
<hymn_number>47</hymn_number>
</song>